Cell["\<\
The rubric for this project is slightly different. Student must complete all \
blue cells in order to receive full credit. There are 16 questions that must \
be answered and 4 Demonstrations. Student grades are still on a scale from \
1-5 but more weight is given to demonstrations than questions.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.756956809006063*^9, 3.756956857394332*^9}, {
